
config LIRE_XENOMAI_SCND_INST
    bool "  Install Xenomai for a _SECOND_ kernel"
    default y
    select LIRE_LINUX_SCND_INST
    help
    Installs the xenomai patch for a *SECOND* kernel. Unselect if you do *NOT* need a second one.
    Unselect also, if you do *NOT* want to have the second one xenomai patched.
